A time-discrete channel with output $$Y_i$$ at time $$i$$, where $$Y_i$$ is the sum of the input $$X_i$$ and the noise $$Z_i$$. The noise is drawn [[i.i.d.]] from a [[Normal distribution]] with [[Variance]] $$N$$